org.apache.flink.runtime.taskmanager

Class TaskCancelResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.taskmanager.AbstractTaskResult
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.taskmanager.TaskCancelResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOReadableWritable

    public class TaskCancelResult
extends AbstractTaskResult
    A TaskCancelResult is used to report the results of a task cancel attempt. It contains the ID of the task to be canceled, a return code and a description. In case of an error during the cancel operation the description includes an error message.
